{"tid":96583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"佔領關愛座行動","createTime":"2017-01-27T03:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T03:39:48.000Z","uid":32486,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"213d66412571e02bc9c703b6f57716f4e2e15138","tid":96583,"uid":32486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"勸大家一上車就坐哂關愛座<br />\n然後由充滿愛心既巴絲打決定讓座比邊啲有需要又值得關愛既人<br />\n咁樣就可以防止啲冇需要既人霸住關愛座唔讓座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地一不讓蔑咀蔑舌廢中 二不讓冇禮貌既廢老 三不讓年不過60扮廢老既廢中<br />\n呢啲人完全唔值得關愛<br />\n<br />\n有人問你點解坐關愛座<br />\n你就話自己係正義既關愛座糾察義工<br />\n叫佢收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d057689e9ef23daef26c06cbb1430e29b5d1f944","tid":96583,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:38:42.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"d394b2bff7fbf16e9c6cf55f315677a767310f32","tid":96583,"uid":57505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:40:14.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"6ea092f70883b4822274e6867fde8cdb0533acf0","tid":96583,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdb11755ac51a796541279292b082c724346a44","tid":96583,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbccc3d3c3274cfe6d308e23d2d65229c0c5b12","tid":96583,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫埋我"},{"pid":"599eb0705c1a1855cb938363c5fad032f3b26ba6","tid":96583,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:39:4